ans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><strong>温馨提示：</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">1、此款奶瓶是标准口，玻璃材质的。奶瓶上配的奶嘴为NUK标准硅胶奶嘴1号中圆孔，适合0-6个月的宝宝喝奶粉使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">2、因为产品外面的刻度是采用的环保油墨不含重金属和添加剂，所以会有掉色的情况，消毒的时候建议把奶瓶倒立，这样可以减少掉色的情况。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">3、每个NUK奶嘴都有换气孔，哺喂时需要将换气孔朝上，在NUK乳胶奶嘴上它的换气孔呈现为一道&rdquo;裂痕状&ldquo;，公司设计就是如此。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><strong>商品特征：</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">1、奶孔方向朝上颚处，宝宝不易呛到，乳汁也可在吞咽前与睡液充分混合，有助于消化吸收。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">2、弧度与宝宝的上颚形状吻合，促使齿颚正常发育。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">3、圆浑的弧度，帮助宝宝吸吮时，下颚可以有如母乳喂哺时般。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\"><strong>注意事项：</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">1、使用前，均先用清水彻底清净，并用消毒锅或置入沸水中不超过5分钟的时间消毒后再使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">2、哺喂时，请先确认奶瓶内的温度，以免烫伤宝宝，同时不可让宝宝单独进食。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">3、每次使用前，均检查奶嘴是否有裂痕或齿痕，如有损坏请立即更新的奶嘴。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">4、勿让宝宝抱着奶瓶边吃边睡，因为食物中的糖份容易造成宝宝蛀牙。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">5、乳胶奶嘴为天然材质，可能会引起过敏反应。遇水或遇热后变大或变白正常现象。不会释放任何有害物质影响健康，但产生粘性或转深褐色即必需更新。（不适用于硅胶或其它物料制造之奶嘴）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">6、玻璃奶瓶可能会破碎。（不适用于塑料奶瓶）</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">7、奶嘴不可以作安抚奶嘴般使用；一般建议的使用效期为：乳胶奶嘴4-6周；硅胶奶嘴8-10周。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">8、如使用奶瓶清洁液，请依照该清洁液制造商的指示使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(107, 107, 107); word-break: break-all; line-height: 24px; font-family: \'arial helvetica sans-serif\';\"><span style=\"font-size: larger;\">9、切勿将奶嘴放置在洗碗机内以清洁剂清洗，以免损毁。</span></p>\r\n<p><img align=\"absmiddle\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 21px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1410934007-0.jpg\" alt=\"\" /><img align=\"absmiddle\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0p