a, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">6.消洗后煮沸消毒2-3分钟，或用NUK奶瓶蒸汽消毒锅消毒。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">7.安抚奶嘴的设计不是全封闭的，能保持它的柔软和顺应性，因此清洗消毒后，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">安抚奶嘴头部有水汽，这是正常现象。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: 