tyle=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">安抚奶嘴在清洗消毒后，如果发现奶嘴内有水泡，&nbsp;这是正常现象，因为安抚奶</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">嘴不是全封闭的，安抚奶嘴的透气系统允许当安抚奶嘴受到婴儿吮吸的压力</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">时，奶嘴中的空气可以释放出来，使得安抚奶嘴变的扁平，以适合婴儿口腔需</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">要。另外，安抚奶嘴头部没有小洞孔，还有后部有口屏档住，安抚奶嘴中间的</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">水汽也不会吸吮到婴儿口内，故使用安抚奶嘴是很安全的</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">有专用的安抚奶嘴链和安抚奶嘴带可栓住安抚奶嘴，方便又安全。有时宝宝不</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">想吮吸安抚奶嘴，吐出来也</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">不</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">会掉到地上，以免弄脏。安抚奶嘴带和安抚奶嘴</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">链的长度安全，不会缠绕到宝宝脖子上，以防出现安全隐患。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">NUK所有安抚奶嘴在出厂前均经过高强度，标准的拉伸测试。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;\">【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;\">注意事项</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt; font-weight: bold;\">】</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">1.使用前，均先用清水彻底洗净，并用消毒锅或置入沸水中不超过5分钟的时间</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">消毒后再使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">勿将安抚奶嘴放置于洗碗机内清洗，以免损坏。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">3.由于NUK安抚奶嘴配有&ldquo;NUK&nbsp;AIR&nbsp;SYSTEM自动进气系统&rdquo;，所以安抚奶嘴消</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">毒</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">后会有水分进奶嘴中，乃正常现象，您仍可放心使用。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">4.每次使用前，特别是宝宝出牙后，均检查安抚奶嘴是否有裂痕或齿痕，如有损</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">坏请立即更换新的安抚奶嘴。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">5.切勿将安抚奶嘴浸泡在甜食或糖水中然后再让宝宝吸吮，因为这样容易造成宝</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">宝蛀牙。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">6.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">千万不要用一根绳子栓住安抚奶嘴，因为普通绳子很容易缠绕婴儿的颈部，引</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">起窒息等不良后果，须用安抚奶嘴链或带。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">7.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">按宝宝的年龄段选取大小合适的安抚奶嘴</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">基于卫生，建议1-2个月即更换新</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">的安抚奶嘴，且每次使用安抚奶嘴的时间亦不宜太长。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">8.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">安抚奶嘴带和安抚奶嘴链除了可栓住安抚奶嘴外还可以栓住其他小玩具，避免</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">玩具掉到地上弄脏。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">9.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">安抚奶嘴盒不是玩具，</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">应放在宝宝无法拿取的地方，且不可将它靠近宝宝的口</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">鼻</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">，以免</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">因意外产生窒息的危险</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">10.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">乳胶安抚奶嘴使用一段时间后，若颜色变暗褐色，说明乳胶巳经老化，需及</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">时更换新的安抚奶嘴。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0pt 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">11.</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15pt;\">硅胶安抚奶嘴如果出现暗纹、牙印或小孔需进行更换，避免碎片被宝宝误</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px;\">食。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin