>3.婴儿喜欢用手抓脸部或身上其他部位，剪好后检查一下指甲缘处有无方角或尖刺，若有应修剪成圆弧形。</p>\r\n<p>4.选择修剪指甲的时间最好选择在喂奶过程中或是等孩子熟睡时。</p>\r\n<p>5.如果指甲下方有污垢，不可用锉刀尖或其他锐利的东西清洗，应在剪完指甲后用水洗干净，以防被感染。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1411094570-0.jpg\" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1411094570-1.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1411094570-2.jpg\" /><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0p